snippet.title: Kenny vs Spenny Versusville - Wasteball Gameplay
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD VERSUSVILLE HERE: https://versusville.com/

Kenny vs Spenny Versusville was a PC game released in 2004 and has been considered lost media ever since 2006 when the show Kenny vs Spenny left the CBC for Showcase & GSN.

On November 4th 2021, Versusville was finally found by Ben, Jphn, Oxymoron, and Myself and is now available for all to download at versusville.com with permission from Kenny Hotz and Mark Greenshields, CEO of DC Studios.
